{
  "stem": "24111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was, for example, an philatelist, and I'm still today a philatelist, because I learned that from him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was the owner of an textile mail order business in Vienna, which he ran with my-- with my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was also under the name of Richard, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Rickert ?] and Josephina Weiss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was located in the Ninth District.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The Ninth District had also an-- a temple, and I believe it was the Mllnergasse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Unfortunately, this temple doesn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was destroyed on the-- during the Crystal Night fires, where all the temples of Vienna were burned and destroyed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Only one survived, which exists still today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The reason of the survival of this particular temple is because it was in the house of the Jewish community, and the Nazis wanted to preserve this particular building, because all the archives and all the activities were done there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that's the reason, actually, this temple survived and exists today.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had a very happy childhood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my childhood ended on March 13, 1938, three days before my 15th birthday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the entry of the Germans and the occupation of Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Hitler came to Austria, and, of course, our life changed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have an older brother by the name of Victor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's two years older than me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went in Vienna to the gimnazjum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he was fortunate to finish it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my childhood ended because on this particular day, we saw an-- we saw the Viennese population out in the streets greeting German troops and German officials in a manner we never saw, we never thought possible before.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was also the first time I heard shouting anti-Semitic remarks, which I actually didn't hear before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, [NON-ENGLISH] Jews, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
